data.description: Great large family home nestled in Hixson, minutes away from shopping, hospital and amazing outdoors activities that Chattanooga has to offer! Upstairs you will find amazing hardwood floors, alongside of a great floor plan. Downstairs could be a separate living space perfect for a a in law or teen suite!  This home offers a state of the art security system. Make your appointment today!
